 *
 * <SCROLL_BEGIN>
 *   [THE FORGE PRINCIPLE]: 
 *   A single AVIS.MZ file is a "Virtual OS Disk." It houses independent 
 *   lanes (|LANG|) which contain full source code for distinct Win32 apps.
 *
 *   [THE ORCHESTRATION PHASES]:
 *   1. EXTRACTION : The C-Loader parses the |LANG| segments into /TEMP/ dirs.
 *   2. COMPILATION: The C-Loader calls the native toolchains (povcc, ml, vb6).
 *   3. LINKAGE    : MERC-G maps the exported .EXEs into a unified Vector Table.
 *   4. EXECUTION  : CYHY launches the apps as a synchronized Application Graph.
 * <SCROLL_END>
 *******************************************************************************/
